{"tid":988500,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「鱔有鱔報！」女主播拿鱔魚塞下體自慰　被判刑1年9個月","createTime":"2019-01-20T06:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-20T07:33:03.000Z","uid":212399,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"71557ec4d81a5a536d3fb2d4adf3cf632ba8fcb4","tid":988500,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:26:27.000Z","msg":"大陸中心／綜合報導<br />\n鱔魚是無辜&hellip;大陸一名女直播主琪琪因「黃鱔門事件」轟動全國，無人不知無人不曉，為了粉絲的大紅包，她竟把黃鱔塞入下體，雖然是私下的特別表演服務，但影片後來被瘋傳，結果現在她得入獄反省，遭判處1年9個月徒刑，獲利不但得全部吐還，還要被罰23萬元（台幣，下同）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/20/1744833-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F20%2F1744833-XXL.jpg&h=0cf80109&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲女直播主琪琪表演「黃鱔塞下體」，遭判1年9個月徒刑。（圖／翻攝微博）<br />\n琪琪在2017年3月，因應大老闆點名要看「黃鱔表演」，還準備了大紅包，她便將活生生的黃鱔放進保險套，然後再塞進下體自慰，「當時那幾個人都是我的VIP，一直跟看我的那幾個人，當時想想就幾個人嘛，就特別開了一個平台，給他們表演一下。」<br />\n原本以為表演完就沒事了，想不到影片被外流，她在同年5月遭到逮捕，獲利全部吐還，更牽出其背後的「老虎」淫穢直播平台，成為大陸公安部督辦的首起網路直播平台傳播淫穢物品牟利案，除了琪琪之外，還有22人被捕，判刑3到10年不等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/20/1744832-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F20%2F1744832-XXL.jpg&h=975d4d66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲琪琪入獄後的模樣。（圖／翻攝新浪網）<br />\n警方查獲「老虎」淫穢直播平台，從2016年12月開始，竟安排超過1千名男女主播進行淫穢表演。用戶只要登錄並儲值，就能向女主播送禮物互動，在線觀看淫穢表演。該直播平台共有100多萬名註冊會員，至今已非法牟利3千多萬元。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/News.aspx?NewsID=487839\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D487839&d=muMOnyiyCXy3iUPhFPTZ5UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=07ed3718\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D487839&h=0027c27a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/News.aspx?NewsID=487839</a>"},{"pid":"42a89f5c099d944313cf5fc21472509e0a884f3d","tid":988500,"uid":55924,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:27:22.000Z","msg":"WTF 個樣爭咁遠既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b7405dc61b991e769601612558bd8ddfda8e59","tid":988500,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:27:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b7ae1c8d938118e30f48ff61bf4f0f157eddc0","tid":988500,"uid":185142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:29:37.000Z","msg":"片呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33a2221a26171df8ea621bb4c4a1bc6798943cf9","tid":988500,"uid":54516,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"42a89f5c099d944313cf5fc21472509e0a884f3d","tid":988500,"uid":55924,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:27:22.000Z","msg":"WTF 個樣爭咁遠既?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:30:34.000Z","msg":"支那直播網/抖陰有filter，點執都得，執到另一個樣都得，男人變女人亦得。"},{"pid":"44249df660743c60c24d518f757069cd2891fe83","tid":988500,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:32:12.000Z","msg":"成個50歲大媽咁款 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd14e7e43cec119750b81d5ccd192380e84f1222","tid":988500,"uid":221265,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:33:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n43UqkN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn43UqkN.jpg&h=44cc5d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1686a2ee842f0993215c88d18a3b2e2475745ed4","tid":988500,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:35:05.000Z","msg":"樓上 more"},{"pid":"30cdb44887cb2793da62ea0d13c6134d54e212e6","tid":988500,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T06:50:25.000Z","msg":"個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d541dc8ef0bda0